{"tid":1246849,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"警方立法會擅自閉門扣留示威者","createTime":"2019-06-21T01:50:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T07:13:30.000Z","uid":132508,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"2aabe4161a541195ca175b66d80ddf9aade0dfdd","tid":1246849,"uid":132508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:50:40.000Z","msg":"From: Charles Mok 莫乃光 facebook                                                                                          影片來源：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CharlesMokOffice/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCharlesMokOffice%2F&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranhx3ZeYPbPBc9Z3MXbd07rU%3D&h=3c678e76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CharlesMokOffice/</a>      <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CharlesMokOffice/videos/443273626453457/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCharlesMokOffice%2Fvideos%2F443273626453457%2F&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranhx3ZeYPbPBc9Z3MXbd07rU%3D&h=53e30eed\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CharlesMokOffice/videos/443273626453457/</a>                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       【還原真相：警方立法會擅自閉門扣留示威者，議員介入被驅趕】 <br />\n<br />\n最近見到有612我和警方理論的影片，但影片根本睇唔到之前發生咩事，所以post返原片比大家睇個來龍去脈，明白我點解會咁激動，去片。<br />\n<br />\n當日我正在做緊訪問，突然聽到有記者大聲話警察係立法會內『審犯』，仲趕埋立法會職員出去，我同Dennis Kwok 郭榮鏗 就即刻衝去了解。我地去到立法會地下大堂接待處後面辦公室，知道有兩個示威者俾警察帶左入房。<br />\n<br />\n立法會保安阻止我地介入，我於是用議員證開門，就見到6、7個警察係入面圍住兩個蜷伏係地下的年青人！呢個係咪符合程序，邊個知道下一步會發生咩事？<br />\n<br />\n我地想確保果兩位示威者的安全，所以我要求留低監察警方行動，質問邊個批准佢地徵用立法會房間閉門鎖住市民！警員在立法會大樓內驅趕我地，係咩道理？<br />\n<br />\n我13/6已經同郭榮鏗議員、譚文豪 Jeremy Tam 議員入信質問立法會主席梁君彥（<a href=\"https://p.charlesmok.hk/2Iu6LYA），\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp.charlesmok.hk%2F2Iu6LYA%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranhx3ZeYPbPBc9Z3MXbd07rU%3D&h=27ce8c2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://p.charlesmok.hk/2Iu6LYA），</a> 要求解答示威者而家情況點樣，究竟警察有無取得批准將立法會當做拘留室？有無諮詢過議員或行管會？（我作為行管會成員冇收過通知）<br />\n<br />\n今日我和郭榮鏗議員去信警務處處長盧偉聰（<a href=\"https://p.charlesmok.hk/2FjYhRK），\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp.charlesmok.hk%2F2FjYhRK%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranhx3ZeYPbPBc9Z3MXbd07rU%3D&h=bd4b5014\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://p.charlesmok.hk/2FjYhRK），</a> 要求交代當日被扣留的兩位市民目前情況，同埋講清楚到底警方將立法會當警署咁閉門審犯有冇越權！"},{"pid":"b995e1df340824ba57fe1195c21d1a870201da24","tid":1246849,"uid":132508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2aabe4161a541195ca175b66d80ddf9aade0dfdd","tid":1246849,"uid":132508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:50:40.000Z","msg":"From: Charles Mok 莫乃光 facebook                                                                                          影片來源：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CharlesMokOffice/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCharlesMokOffice%2F&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranhx3ZeYPbPBc9Z3MXbd07rU%3D&h=3c678e76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CharlesMokOffice/</a>      <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CharlesMokOffice/videos/443273626453457/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCharlesMokOffice%2Fvideos%2F443273626453457%2F&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranhx3ZeYPbPBc9Z3MXbd07rU%3D&h=53e30eed\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CharlesMokOffice/videos/443273626453457/</a>                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              