事？<br />\n<br />\n我地想確保果兩位示威者的安全，所以我要求留低監察警方行動，質問邊個批准佢地徵用立法會房間閉門鎖住市民！警員在立法會大樓內驅趕我地，係咩道理？<br />\n<br />\n我13/6已經同郭榮鏗議員、譚文豪 Jeremy Tam 議員入信質問立法會主席梁君彥（<a href=\"https://p.charlesmok.hk/2Iu6LYA），\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp.charlesmok.hk%2F2Iu6LYA%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranhx3ZeYPbPBc9Z3MXbd07rU%3D&h=27ce8c2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://p.charlesmok.hk/2Iu6LYA），</a> 要求解答示威者而家情況點樣，究竟警察有無取得批准將立法會當做拘留室？有無諮詢過議員或行管會？（我作為行管會成員冇收過通知）<br />\n<br />\n今日我和郭榮鏗議員去信警務處處長盧偉聰（<a href=\"https://p.charlesmok.hk/2FjYhRK），\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp.charlesmok.hk%2F2FjYhRK%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranhx3ZeYPbPBc9Z3MXbd07rU%3D&h=bd4b5014\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://p.charlesmok.hk/2FjYhRK），</a> 要求交代當日被扣留的兩位市民目前情況，同埋講清楚到底警方將立法會當警署咁閉門審犯有冇越權！"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:53:10.000Z","msg":"唔知點解莫乃光尋日見先放呢段片出黎? 而家警察真係痴線到極點!! 唔知入面個兩個人而家點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T03:24:53.000Z","msg":"應該唔係尋日先放，我好似前日定再早一日睇過"},{"pid":"69b232c1211ad805c2f7ce446674847addb75a9c","tid":1246849,"uid":181535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T03:29:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b86382cec7d0c64d092009f9860ac1d765afe3c","tid":1246849,"uid":132508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28b5344e0e4bf706177d9246584e8d80617c7a5d","tid":1246849,"uid":1712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b995e1df340824ba57fe1195c21d1a870201da24","tid":1246849,"uid":132508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2aabe4161a541195ca175b66d80ddf9aade0dfdd","tid":1246849,"uid":132508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:50:40.000Z","msg":"From: Charles Mok 莫乃光 facebook                                                                                          影片來源：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CharlesMokOffice/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u